description: For sale: $235,000. Welcome to this beautiful old-world charm 4 bedroom home. Located only a block away from the green line transportation center! This home offers a tasteful blend of original hardwood flooring, impressive French doors, and tall solid wood base trim throughout combined with today's modern amenities everyone wants in their home. Including an upgraded kitchen with higher end stainless steel appliances, huge pantry, new granite counters and custom backsplash. Don't miss the remodeled bathroom, stained glass windows that are sure to be a conversation piece, and the huge front porch ready to enjoy your stay at home order with a morning coffee and evening chatting. You do not want to miss this charming vintage gem!

For sale: $373,500. Outstanding! Merriam Park 1900 solid classic home combines gorgeous original architecture with seamless modern additions. Formal living/dining room
showcases a stunning open staircase accented w/unique quarter-sawn oak pillars/balusters, brick fireplace framed w/leaded glass windows/bookcases and
hardwood flrs. Updated kitchen opens to beautiful light-filled sunroom/informal dining area addition. Main floor 1/2 bath/mudroom greets attached garage
off kitchen. Porch, paver patio and fenced yard complete w/perennial garden, pergola and honeysuckle vines add entertaining/relaxation in summer. Three
upper-level bedrooms, one of which is an abundant sun-splashed 19'x19' room w/windows on all 4 sides! Unfinished lower level offers flex room,
laundry/utility room and old school dark room-easily convertible to storage. Many newer items-roof, furnace, windows and two fabulous additions-make this
lovely home a rare find. Turn-key and well-maintained, this Merriam Park gem won't last long!

For sale: $280,000. Classic up/down duplex is just a couple of blocks to the light rail, Victoria Station, Allianz Field, several Universities and major highways. Main level unit offers a 3 season porch, 3 bedrooms, a full bath and a very spacious living/dining room area with beautiful hardwood floors. This unit has interior access to a storage room and its own washer/dryer in the lower level. Upper level offers 2 bedrooms, a large walk-in closet, a stackable washer & dryer and a sunroom. This unit also has a storage room in the lower level with exterior access in the back of the duplex. There is an out-building currently used for storage. Plenty of parking is available on the driveway for 4 cars or possibly more. This property sits on a double lot. The side yard offers green space for entertaining or play! Great opportunity for investors or owner occupant!

Recently sold: $430,000. This spacious 3-bedroom, 3-bath condominium combines century-old craftsmanship with fresh design and convenience.  It features outstanding oak woodwork throughout, including five-piece crown moldings, a built-in buffet, beveled glass bookcases, a beamed ceiling in the formal dining room and newly refinished oak and birch flooring.  The remodeled eat-in kitchen boasts granite counters, top-of-the line stainless appliances (Bosch, LG, Capital), new birch flooring and cherry cabinetry.  A gas fireplace anchors the living room. The generously sized master suite includes a walk-in closet with custom cherry shelving and a three-quarter master bath with newly refinished hardwood floors.
